{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778463761405,"sessionID":"ses_1eb4d6de0ffeGwqt7F6lQ5EDP7","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:34","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","content":"## Summary\n\nThis PR obsoletes GO:0008785 alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity and replaces it with GO:0102039 NADH-dependent peroxiredoxin activity, per issue #31961.\n\n### Changes made\n\n1. **GO:0008785 — obsoleted**\n   - Prefix `name` with `obsolete`\n   - Prefix `def` with `OBSOLETE.`\n   - Added `comment: The reason for obsoletion is that it is more specific than the specificity of any known gene product.`\n   - Removed `is_a: GO:0016668`\n   - Added `property_value: term_tracker_item` pointing to issue #31961\n   - Added `is_obsolete: true`\n   - Added `replaced_by: GO:0102039`\n\n2. **GO:0009321 alkyl hydroperoxide reductase complex — comment updated**\n   - Changed the cross-referenced molecular function from the obsolete term to the replacement: `NADH-dependent peroxiredoxin activity ; GO:0102039`\n\n3. **GO:0070937 CRD-mediated mRNA stability complex — erroneous comment removed**\n   - Removed a spurious comment that incorrectly referenced `alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity ; GO:0008785`. This had no biological relevance to the mRNA stability complex.\n\n### Checklist\n\n- [x] Issue intent analyzed and plan created\n- [x] Relevant terms searched in ontology\n- [x] All references to the obsolete term removed or updated\n- [x] Obsolete term has correct metadata (no logical axioms, correct name/def, replaced_by)\n- [x] Term tracker items added\n- [x] Changes committed to `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`\n\n### Validation\n\nBasic OBO structural validation was performed. No new errors were introduced. Note that `robot` / `make travis_build` were not available in this environment.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778463761401,"end":1778463761404}},"id":"prt_e14b35d30001yG0m2qybiEBhJC","sessionID":"ses_1eb4d6de0ffeGwqt7F6lQ5EDP7","messageID":"msg_e14b356e7001ax4I2NFGthPWd8"}}
